# 密码输入框



# 示例 🤔


# 基础

引入 t-password-input 组件并传入 values 即可

<template>
	<view>
		<view class="mx-2">
            <t-password-input :values="values" @click="open"/>
        </view>

        <t-number-key-board v-model="values" ref="nk" />
	</view>
</template>

<script>
    export default {
        data() {
            return {
                values: ''
            }
        },
        methods: {
            open() {
                this.$refs.nk.show()
            }
        }
    }
</script>


# 可见

让 visible 为 true 即可

<template>
	<view>
		<view class="mx-2">
				<t-password-input :values="values" visible @click="open"/>
			</view>

        <t-number-key-board v-model="values" ref="nk" />
	</view>
</template>

<script>
    export default {
        data() {
            return {
                values: ''
            }
        },
        methods: {
            open() {
                this.$refs.nk.show()
            }
        }
    }
</script>

full | 3xl | 2xl |
xl | lg | md | base | sm | none
